# Implementation Plan - Upload Resource Page

Implement a premium, responsive "Upload Resource" page for the TRC Platform.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The design specifies a multi-step workflow. I will implement a reactive step system to manage Metadata, Authors, and Files sections.

## Proposed Changes

### Resource Module

#### [MODIFY] [UploadResource.vue](file:///c:/Users/hlina/Desktop/TRCPROJECT/frontend/src/modules/resource/pages/UploadResource.vue)
- Implement the main page layout using `DashboardLayout`.
- Add a multi-step indicator (Steppers) following the design (1-5 steps).
- Create sections for:
    - **Resource Metadata**: Inputs for Title, Category (Select), Primary Institution (Select), Abstract (Textarea), and Keywords (Tag input).
    - **Authors & Contributors**: A list view of added authors with roles and an "Add Author" button.
    - **File Upload**: A drag-and-drop zone with file details and progress bar.
- Implement responsive layout:
    - **Tablet**: Vertical stack of sections.
    - **Desktop**: Main form on the left, auxiliary panels (File summary, Submission tips) on the right.
- Add footer actions: "Save Draft", "Cancel", and "Next Step".

